overview: So much fresh meat, so little time! Quentin Gainz is back to show new recruit Johnny what bottoming is all about! He was nervous at first, but as they got into the swing of things, this newbie showed his natural talents! Ivan James goes 'all in' with first timer Will. These two have real chemistry together and it shows. Lastly we have to new recruits, Justin Grey and Jason who give us a front row seat as they stroke their massive man bones until they shoot their loads and smile for the camera! Enjoy!
title: Battle of the Bottoms 3
